24. Model Governance Notes
This model is a macro overlay and diagnostic engine. It is not a standalone return-maximizing strategy.
It should be governed as:
•	a regime classification module
•	a risk filter
•	a portfolio overlay input
•	a dashboard component
It should not be interpreted as a standalone prediction engine for precise short-term market direction.
