Data validation
•	required columns present
•	no duplicate dates
•	date index sorted
•	no impossible price values
Feature validation
•	ratios behave as expected
•	drawdowns are bounded correctly
•	z-scores do not explode from zero variance
•	VIX features behave directionally correctly
Scoring validation
•	score rises during credit improvement
•	score falls during stress events
